intent.user_query: Which products are most frequently purchased together in the same order?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT  p1.ProductName AS Product1, p2.ProductName AS Product2, COUNT(*) AS Frequency FROM  fitness_db.OrderItems oi1 JOIN  fitness_db.OrderItems oi2 ON oi1.OrderID = oi2.OrderID AND oi1.ProductID < oi2.ProductID JOIN  fitness_db.Products p1 ON oi1.ProductID = p1.ProductID JOIN  fitness_db.Products p2 ON oi2.ProductID = p2.ProductID GROUP BY  p1.ProductName, p2.ProductName ORDER BY  Frequency DESC TOP 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT  p1.ProductName AS Product1, p2.ProductName AS Product2, COUNT(*) AS Frequency FROM  fitness_db.OrderItems oi1 JOIN  fitness_db.OrderItems oi2 ON oi1.OrderID = oi2.OrderID AND oi1.ProductID < oi2.ProductID JOIN  fitness_db.Products p1 ON oi1.ProductID = p1.ProductID JOIN  fitness_db.Products p2 ON oi2.ProductID = p2.ProductID GROUP BY  p1.ProductName, p2.ProductName ORDER BY  Frequency DESC TOP 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
